title: Five Biggest Names That Could Move by the Trade Deadline | Group Chat
description:
Justin and Rob are joined by Steve Jones Jr. of the Dunker Spot Podcast to discuss the biggest names that could be moved by this Thursday’s trade deadline, including Kyle Lowry (02:00), Lonzo Ball (09:00), Aaron Gordon (16:00), and more.
Host: Justin Verrier and Rob Mahoney
Guest: Steve Jones Jr.
